title: Electronicaz - Discotronic 2008 Demo
description:
Very early-stages demo of the brand new ELECTRONICAZ tune "Discotronic" take one at 01.16 hrs UK time 25Sep08. 

This tune pays homage to the movie TRON and the arcade game Discs of Tron. I spent weeks of my holidays back in the 80s playing that game.... and now I have my closure..... or should that be vengeance!

By veteran music-maker Love Groove aka Bat Country aka Gorejuice aka ELECTRONICAZ.

Check myspace dot com slash electronicaz  for more info.

Cheers!
